## QUICK CHECKS BEFORE COMMITTING

**For Models:**

- [ ]  Interface has `I` prefix
- [ ]  timestamps: true
- [ ]  Explicit collection name
- [ ]  Indexes on frequently queried fields
- [ ]  Validation messages on all required fields

**For Services:**

- [ ]  Explicit return type
- [ ]  Named export
- [ ]  Custom errors (never mongoose errors)
- [ ]  Uses `.exec()` on queries
- [ ]  No req/res access

**For Endpoints:**

- [ ]  Three files: types.ts, schema.ts, handler.ts
- [ ]  Uses matchedData()
- [ ]  Calls ONE service only
- [ ]  Try-catch with next(error)
- [ ]  Router has checkSchema + schemaCheck

**For All Code:**

- [ ]  Path aliases used
- [ ]  No default exports
- [ ]  Explicit returns
- [ ]  TypeScript strict mode compliant